Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(960,636)}令正義伸張 哪怕天堂墜落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.82,0:00:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,劣等的地球民族 別以為你能逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,打敗了布拉德騎士的重甲騎兵是一架橙色的機體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,地球人都是敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是你駕駛Sky Carrier將Argyre運送過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你說得沒錯…他確實是被橙色的那個滑鬼頭給打敗了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,輸給了地球重甲騎兵的軌道騎士只有兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,布拉德騎士和托利爾蘭男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,而在托利爾蘭男爵敗北的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,亞瑟拉姆公主和地球的橙色機體在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,根據Sky Carrier的數據顯示
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,搭載著那架機體的船朝著西南偏南方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.43,0:00:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有確切的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,也許這也只是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.42,0:01:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 目前手中的線索也只有這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我的哥哥也參加了種子島的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.03,0:01:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他戰死了 不…準確地說是被你給殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,馬格巴麗吉是我養父的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我的舊姓是休穆雷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你的摯友就是我的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.29,0:01:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,上空的敵機 急速下降
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,側翼也有3機在逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.64,0:01:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這是直擊艦橋的路線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,命中！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,最後1個！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沒子彈了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,艦長…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？我還活著？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他到底打算把我愚弄到什麼地步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我用Tharsis出擊 給我準備Sky Carrier！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,且慢 庫魯迪歐伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,扎赫巴姆伯爵 為什麼要阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你說讓我活捉他的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他發現你追擊他而改變目的地的話 事情反而不好辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道那傢伙到底要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,您這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你認為那傢伙是為了什麼而使用謁見室的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他是間諜 就一定會有同夥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我會從上空追蹤他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人的增援？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他阻止了對我們的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,內訌？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也許只是在爭奪獵物而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣都好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那是敵人的敵人 就算不是同伴也有利用價值
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是哪一族敢來妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這片土地已經是我費米安的領土了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1074,985)}Femieanne
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不允許你在我的領地上肆意妄為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 我的眷屬們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,布提斯的手指…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(850.5,985)}Botis
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.69,NOTE,,0,0,0,,{\an7}註：布提斯 所羅門72柱魔神中排第17位的魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,鞠戶上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,鞠戶上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,休穆雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,抓緊我 休穆雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,鞠戶…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,休穆雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在就救你出來 休穆雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,完全打不中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,它拉開了距離 也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,控制塔！打開船塢式機庫！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是Mustang-22的請求！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,艦長！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,界冢的弟弟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,摀住耳朵！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 請摀住耳朵！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:13.03,INEN,,0,0,0,,Share me your madness that you keep in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.73,INEN,,0,0,0,,Show that you're scared like me Thus we are teens
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:19.13,INEN,,0,0,0,,Wash my hands of that for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:22.22,INEN,,0,0,0,,Sell myself for this hopeless loop
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:29.72,INEN,,0,0,0,,May I have seen your face somewhere sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.36,INEN,,0,0,0,,You freeze my blood and spine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:32.80,INEN,,0,0,0,,So freak me out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.02,INEN,,0,0,0,,Like a look in a mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.96,INEN,,0,0,0,,Face my Doppelgäger
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:40.07,INEN,,0,0,0,,How 'bout you? Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:45.38,INEN,,0,0,0,,Beware of attentions, entourages and mates
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.53,0:08:47.99,INEN,,0,0,0,,You are what you do
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:53.31,INEN,,0,0,0,,Depress your metions, ain't got to be a bighead
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:56.79,INEN,,0,0,0,,You are what you fool
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:57.72,INEN,,0,0,0,,Right now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.67,INEN,,0,0,0,,Burn your soul, neck or nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:02.80,INEN,,0,0,0,,Burn it out 'til you're losing your reason
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:05.53,INEN,,0,0,0,,Forget the stoned reason to drive it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.54,INEN,,0,0,0,,Just to scribe your existence
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.57,INEN,,0,0,0,,Not a crime, your insistence
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:12.91,INEN,,0,0,0,,Die another day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:13.51,INEN,,0,0,0,,So do I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.67,INEN,,0,0,0,,Burn my soul, all to nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:19.01,INEN,,0,0,0,,Burn it out, let me charge in your advance
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:21.63,INEN,,0,0,0,,I'm watching for the chance to beat it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:23.61,INEN,,0,0,0,,Even though my body's shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:25.60,INEN,,0,0,0,,I'll give it all, deadly bumping
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:28.59,INEN,,0,0,0,,Cuz you make me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.35,INEN,,0,0,0,,Breathless
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,隱藏的船塢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,引擎呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,還能動！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,船體呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,勉勉強強…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不 已經開始進水了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,衝入前方的船塢裏去！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,全…全速前進！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我說…伊奈帆!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mustang-11！我們也跟上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,阿奈 你自作主張打算做什麼…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,雪姐你呢 船的護衛要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,機槍掃射！目標 門閘上方的岩石！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算做什麼…橙色的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我們去幹掉那架三頭六臂機體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,本揚陸城既將進入可掃瞄日本列島的區域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,只要進入了掃瞄區域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就立刻搜索斯雷因·托羅亞特所奪取的那架Sky Carrier
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,亞瑟拉姆公主其實還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我是親眼見證的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,扎赫巴姆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,已經發現了那架機體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,它現在在日本列島西南的種子島上空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好像正在和費米安伯爵的重甲騎兵Hellas交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然在種子島？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我從來沒聽說過種子島上有這樣的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,總之 抓緊時間退艦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧 鞠戶上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,別擠！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,盡可能不要吸入煙霧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,優先讓非戰鬥人員去避難
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,緊接著是傷兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人都不要落下！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:10:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,祭陽前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mustang小隊呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,韻子他們不在甲板上！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他們還在外面戰鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,為了讓我們有時間逃走 在外面充當誘餌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,命中！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來 右3密爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要攻擊強襲艦就必須打碎岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,想提升威力就有必要先提升速度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,火箭想要加速 必然需要一定的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,距離一長 只要角度稍有偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,瞄準就會出現巨大的偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,4點鐘方向出現敵機！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,它正朝著這邊前進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:12:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,火星的攻擊機會保護我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼回事啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,雪姐 直接去攻擊敵人的重甲騎兵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊？不可能贏得了那種東西的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,難說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,也許只是虛有其表而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,韻子 手槍借我一用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,第11、12區域已確認退艦完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,第8區域的退艦工作也結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來全員就都齊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我們也趕緊離開這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,能和Mustang小隊取得聯絡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,只能祈禱他們平安無事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,馬格巴麗吉艦長！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不見笑 不是讓你帶著難民去避難嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經讓他們暫時到前面的貨倉裏避難了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我有件東西想讓艦長看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我的錯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因為我來了地球嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我沒來 就不會發生暗殺事件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這場戰爭就不會發生…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,人們也不會有這種殘酷遭遇…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,記住 對這些人而言 火星人都是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我也毫無頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏到底是用來做什麼的設施啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:13:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,公…公主殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,您要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…火星的重甲騎兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是隕石坑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,落到這裏的隕石並不只有一塊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一塊撞擊在海岸形成了海灣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,另一塊就落在了這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼這架機體就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 這就是15年前的惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為Heavens Fall已經把他們全部抹殺了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這還真是感動的再會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是說這傢伙被俘獲了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 是為了隱藏這個事實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,鞠戶上尉所寫的種子島報告才會石沉大海的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真的就這麼簡單嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:14:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,馬格巴麗吉艦長！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,看那兒！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這到底是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,橙色的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 阿奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,從剛剛開始 那台三頭六臂就一直待在那裏沒有動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,只是在用同樣的手段進行著攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我想那傢伙的武器肯定只有那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你們掩護我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 阿奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,伊奈帆！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你在開玩笑吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,開啟接觸回路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我們長話短說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你那邊的裝備還剩下多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,榴彈炮還剩下20發左右
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,HE彈還剩下9發 我身上就只有這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,阿奈 快回來！那是火星的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 雪姐 一會兒再和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hellas的拳頭會通過巨大分子化來增強自身強度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是什麼樣的子彈都無法破壞它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不 有個拳頭已經被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,大概它的手指活動的時候分子構造會變回原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,將安定裝置的信號傳到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(762,985)}stabilizer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的規格可是不一樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,無所謂 我會進行解析的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,它來了 蝙蝠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,蝙蝠？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:38.07,INEN,,0,0,0,,Unknown soldier lying on the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.43,INEN,,0,0,0,,Explosions forever
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:44.42,INEN,,0,0,0,,Now you take me away from danger
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:47.93,INEN,,0,0,0,,We had always covered up your face
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.30,INEN,,0,0,0,,Out there who will watch your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:54.33,INEN,,0,0,0,,Because I don't know if I can stay here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:56.10,INEN,,0,0,0,,Game over
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:59.45,INEN,,0,0,0,,Now we hate our brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:03.29,INEN,,0,0,0,,No longer can move my feet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:04.11,INEN,,0,0,0,,But it's
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:05.84,INEN,,0,0,0,,Keep on keeping on
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:08.08,INEN,,0,0,0,,And it's I just wanna know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:10.88,INEN,,0,0,0,,Inside it's I don't want to know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:14.22,INEN,,0,0,0,,Over head they fly high it's going
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.94,INEN,,0,0,0,,On and on and on
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:20.98,INEN,,0,0,0,,Will we oversee the smile of love and peace for everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:22.99,INEN,,0,0,0,,You can be sure
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:24.73,INEN,,0,0,0,,I'll be back again
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:53.72,INEN,,0,0,0,,But it's
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.32,INEN,,0,0,0,,Keep on keeping on
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:57.84,INEN,,0,0,0,,And it's I just wanna know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.33,INEN,,0,0,0,,Inside it's I don't want to know
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:03.74,INEN,,0,0,0,,Over head they fly high it's going
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:05.43,INEN,,0,0,0,,On and on and on
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:10.61,INEN,,0,0,0,,Will we oversee the smile of love and peace for everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:12.43,INEN,,0,0,0,,You can be sure
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.60,INEN,,0,0,0,,I'll be back again
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:26.07,INEN,,0,0,0,,And I remember a long time ago
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:28.59,INEN,,0,0,0,,I will be there for you and please wait for me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:30.88,INEN,,0,0,0,,Oh you must believe me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:33.80,INEN,,0,0,0,,Better you believe your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:38.74,INEN,,0,0,0,,I will be there for you and please wait for me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:41.25,INEN,,0,0,0,,Oh you must believe me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:44.17,INEN,,0,0,0,,Better you believe your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,摩拉克斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(931.5,985)}Marax
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.00,NOTE,,0,0,0,,{\an9}註：摩拉克斯 所羅門72柱魔神中排名第21位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子還是一樣愛亂來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我們繼續前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,放著他不管可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的 那孩子每次亂來的結果基本上都是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:16:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,引到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,另一架 從後方跟緊它！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果攻擊後方無裝甲的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以打到它的引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,後方又出現了2機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,方向175 沿著海岸線來飛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,雪姐 能聽到我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,把我呼之即來揮之即去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,方向保持不變！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,布提斯…摩拉克斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(795,985)}Botis
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1045.5,985)}Marax
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,羅諾比 …哈帕斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(816,985)}Ronove
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1051.5,985)}Halphas
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,勞姆…拜恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:42.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(847.5,985)}Raum
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:42.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1017,985)}Vine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢傷害我的孩子們…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,同時攻擊哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 就拿出我的殺手鑭！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,飛走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,它拉開了距離 開始加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,用狙擊打偏它的軌道！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼大的體型用步槍是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,現在掛著你 機體太沉了躲不開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看我把你們撞散
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,它來了 蝙蝠！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,給我閉嘴 橙色的傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然躲開了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,讓機體失速下降了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,拉不起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,同樣的手段對我可行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,飛空艇？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是戰艦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,找到你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,亞瑟拉姆公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有Aldnoah的地球人為什麼會駕駛著這樣的戰艦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,12點鐘方向敵機接近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這是碰撞路線！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡的地球人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,請準備應對衝擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 還沒結束！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的火星人都是我父親的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我們成功了呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,終於找到你了 亞瑟拉姆公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,公主已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 你為什麼還在找她？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道公主還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這是為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你這話是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,請讓我和公主見一面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,先回答我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,難道…你想利用公主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我要利用她 你有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的敵人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:21:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.05,0:22:11.05,TITLE,,0,0,0,,「二人的邂逅」

